(Republished)

Henrietta Davis, Appellant, v. Halo Realty Corp. et al., Respondents.

— Order, entered on February 24, 1965, unanimously affirmed, with $50 costs and disbursements to the respondents. The order of this court entered on May 10, 1966 (25 A D 2d 951) is vacated. No opinion.

Concur — Botein, P. J., McNally, Stevens and Steuer, JJ.
